quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  50,27,"Mnzake adzanena kuti, “Ambuye wathu! Ine sindidamuuze kuti aziswa malamulo ayi koma iye adadzisocheretsa yekha.”"
  50,28,"Mulungu adzati, “Musakangane pamaso panga. Ine ndidakutumizirani chenjezo lokwanira.”"
  50,29,Chilango sichisintha ayi ndipo Ine sindionetsa chinyengo kwa akapolo anga
  50,30,"Patsiku limene Ife tidzaifunsa Gahena kuti, “Kodi mwadzadza?” Ndipo iyo idzati, “Kodi akanalipobe ena?”"
  50,31,Ndipo Paradiso idzabweretsedwa kufupi kwa anthu olungama
  50,32,Ichi ndicho chimene mudalonjezedwa ndipo ndi mphotho kwa iye amene amadzipereka kwa Mulungu nthawi zonse nasunga malamulo ake
  50,33,Ndiponso kwa iye amene amaopa Mwini chisoni chosatha wosaoneka ndipo amadza kwa Iye ndi mtima wodzichepetsa
  50,34,Lowani m’menemo mwamtendere ndi mosaopa ayi. Ili ndi tsiku la moyo wosatha
  50,35,M’menemo mudzakhala chilichonse chimene iwo adzafuna ndipo Ife tili ndi zinthu zambiri
  50,36,Kodi ndi mibadwo ingati imene Ife tidaiononga iwo asanabadwe amene adali ndi mphamvu zoposa iwo ndipo iwo adafuna chitetezo padziko? Kodi iwo anali ndi kwina kothawira
  50,37,Ndithudi muli chikumbutso mu zimenezi kwa iye amene ali ndi mtima kapena amatchera khutu pamene achenjezedwa
  50,38,Ndithudi Ife tidalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zili m’menemo m’masiku asanu ndi limodzi ndipo sitidatope ayi
  50,39,Kotero pirira pa zonse zimene amanena ndipo lemekeza Ambuye wako dzuwa lisanatuluke ndiponso lisanalowe
  50,40,Ndipo mulemekeze Iye usiku ndipo utatha kupemphera
  50,41,Ndipo udzamve patsiku limene woitana adzaitana kuchokera pafupi
  50,42,Tsiku limene iwo adzamva kulira kwa mfuwu woona. Limeneli lidzakhala tsiku louka kwa akufa
  50,43,Ndithudi ndife amene timapereka moyo ndi imfa ndipo ndi kwa Ife kumene zonse zidzabwerera
  50,44,Tsiku limene dziko lidzang’ambika ndipo iwo adzatuluka mofulumira. Kumeneko ndiko kudzakhala kusonkhanitsidwa pamodzi
  50,45,Ife timadziwa zonse zimene amanena ndipo iwe si ndiwe wankhanza ayi. Koma muchenjeze ndi Korani kwa aliyense amene aopa chilango changa
  51,1,Pali mphepo imene imamwaza fumbi
  51,2,Ndi mitambo imene ili yolemedwa ndi madzi
  51,3,Ndi zombo zimene zimayenda mosavutika ndi mwabata
  51,4,Ndipo pali iwo amene amagawa madalitso ndi chilolezo chathu
  51,5,"Ndithudi chimene mwalonjezedwa, ndithudi, ndi choona"
  51,6,Ndithudi chiweruzo chidzakwaniritsidwa
  51,7,Pali kumwamba kumene kuli njira zambiri
  51,8,Ndithudi inu muli ndi maganizo osiyana
  51,9,Amene abwezedwa ku icho ndiye amene wabwezedwa
  51,10,wotembereredwa akhale amene amanama
  51,11,Amene akutidwa ndi kusamvera
  51,12,"Iwo amafunsa kuti, “Kodi tsiku lachiweruzo lidzadza liti?”"
  51,13,"Tsiku limene iwo adzaweruzidwa ndi kuponyedwa ku Zariat\t559 moto"
  51,14,Lawani chilango chanu! Ichi ndicho chimene munali kufuna kuti chidze msanga
  51,15,Ndithudi iwo amene amalewa machimo adzakhala m’minda imene ili ndi a kasupe
  51,16,Kulandira zimene Ambuye wawo awapatsa. Ndithudi kale iwo anali kuchita zinthu zabwino
  51,17,Iwo anali kugona nthawi yochepa usiku
  51,18,Ndipo m’bandakucha anali kupempha chikhululukiro
  51,19,Ndipo mu chuma chawo mudali gawo limene linali kuperekedwa kwa anthu opempha ndi osowa
  51,20,Ndipo m’dziko muli zizindikiro kwa iwo okhulupirira
  51,21,Ndi mizimu yanu kodi simungaone
  51,22,Ndipo kumwamba ndiko kuli chakudya chanu ndi zimene muli kulonjezedwa
  51,23,"Ndiye, pali Ambuye wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi, chimenechi ndi cholinga ndi choonadi chomwe inu mumayankhula"
  51,24,Kodi udamva nkhani ya alendo olemekezeka a Abrahamu
  51,25,"Pamene iwo adadza kwa iye, iwo adati, “Mtendere.” Ndipo iye adati, “Mtendere.” Ndipo iye adati, “Inu ndinu alendo kwa ine.”"
  51,26,Ndipo iye atapita ku banja lake adabweretsa nyama ya ng’ombe yowotcha
  51,27,"Motero iye adadza nayo kwa iwo nati, “Kodi simufuna kudya?”"
  51,28,"Motero iye adayamba kuchita mantha mu mtima mwake. Ndipo iwo adati, “Usaope.” Ndipo iwo adamuuza nkhani yabwino yakubadwa kwa mwana wamwamuna yemwe adzakhala wanzeru kwambiri"
  51,29,"Ndipo mkazi wake adadza modzichepetsa ndipo adamenya pa mphumi pake nati, “Nkhalamba yaikazi yosaberekapo!”"
  51,30,"Iwo adati, “Ngakhale ndi choncho, Ambuye wako wayankhula. Iye ndi wodzala ndi luntha ndiponso nzeru.”"